    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The evaluation of proposals for development or for changes to existing structures or spaces, typically by a board representing the community where the activity is to take place.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
